++### 问题 2: 授权后仍然显示需要授权
++
++**检查点**:
++1. OAuth 回调是否正确保存 refresh_token
++2. `needs_reauth` 字段是否设置为 0
++
++```sql
++SELECT refresh_token, needs_reauth, authorized_at 
++FROM google_ads_user_oauth_bindings 
++WHERE user_id = 1;
++```
++
++如果 `needs_reauth` 仍然是 1，手动更新：
++
++```sql
++UPDATE google_ads_user_oauth_bindings 
++SET needs_reauth = 0 
++WHERE user_id = 1;
++```
